- **Video Manager Table**: List all uploaded videos. Each row has: thumbnail, title, views, visibility badge, publish date, and action buttons (`Edit`, [Delete](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/dashboard/page.tsx#66-79)).
- **Quick Upload CTA**: "Upload Your Next Video" button.
