### Phase 12: Playback Recovery & Shorts Population
Address the critical blockers identified during the audit.

#### [MODIFY] [app/HomeClient.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/HomeClient.tsx) & [app/watch/[id]/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Walt%20&%20Carter/.gemini/antigravity/playground/sonic-zenith/app/watch/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx)
- **Resilient Queries**: Remove `quality_score`, `is_live`, and `category` from direct Supabase `.select()` if they are causing 400 errors, or ensure they are added to the DB.
- **Watch Page Fix**: Re-verify the `await params` logic and add even more detailed error logging to catch production-specific environmental issues.

#### [NEW] SQL (Consolidated Fix)
```sql
-- Add quality_score if missing to prevent 400 errors
ALTER TABLE public.videos ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS quality_score FLOAT DEFAULT 0.5;
-- Ensure is_short is present
ALTER TABLE public.videos ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS is_short BOOLEAN DEFAULT false;
-- Add missing columns found during audit
ALTER TABLE public.videos ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS is_live BOOLEAN DEFAULT false;
ALTER TABLE public.videos ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS category TEXT DEFAULT 'General';
```

